Program has

202
00:14:16,569 --> 00:14:21,182
sold sodium hypochlorite to households in
rural Haiti since 2002.

203
00:14:22,410 --> 00:14:28,170
The program began at the Missions of Love
health clinic, in Jolivert northern Haiti.

204
00:14:28,170 --> 00:14:32,570
And since 2008, it has been managed by the
NGO, Deep Springs International.

205
00:14:33,670 --> 00:14:37,560
The program makes its own chlorine through
electrolysis of salt water.

206
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:42,210
Which is branded as Gadyen Dlo, meaning
