207
00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:46,260
Project team members enroll families by
selling safe

208
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:52,250
storage containers or Bokit Espesyal with
lids and taps.

209
00:14:52,250 --> 00:14:56,690
The team also sells bottles of Gadyen Dlo
keeping sales records for each family.

210
00:14:56,690 --> 00:15:02,430
And conducts regular household visits to
monitor use and provide ongoing education.

211
00:15:03,860 --> 00:15:08,760
One bottles costs about $1.25 and contains
